課程概述 Course Description
       本課程在於使學生瞭解軌道運輸系統業經營管理之特性如：安全管理、營運管理與維修管理、風險管理以及營收管理等專業知識。This course introduces some essential management techniques in railway operation such as safety management, yield management, scheduling, etc. In addition, the instructor also organizes some field trips in the local railway organization.     

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    This course aims to provide the expertise and understanding of the railway system operation and management.
     

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Railway and Transport2Policy and Legislation3Cost and pricing4Forecast of Rail Demand(I)5Forecast of Rail Demand(II)6Expert presentation 7field trip8Planning and Management of Railways9mid term exam 10Railway revenue management(I)11Railway revenue management(II)12Railway safety system management(I)13Railway safety system management(II)14Train dispatching and scheduling15Expert presentation 16field trip17Final report 18Final report 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


