週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Railway and Transport2Policy and Legislation3Cost and pricing4Forecast of Rail Demand(I)5Forecast of Rail Demand(II)6Expert presentation 7field trip8Planning and Management of Railways9mid term exam 10Railway revenue management(I)11Railway revenue management(II)12Railway safety system management(I)13Railway safety system management(II)14Train dispatching and scheduling15Expert presentation 16field trip17Final report 18Final report 

